Package: pmatools
Title: GRADE Certainty Assessment from Meta-Analysis Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yuki", "Furukawa", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Assess certainty of evidence (GRADE) from meta-analysis objects
    produced by the {meta} package, following the BMJ 2025 Core GRADE series
    (Guyatt et al.). Automatically evaluates inconsistency (I², tau², Q-test),
    imprecision (CI width, OIS), and publication bias (Egger's test / registry
    check). Risk of bias (weight-based domination flowchart) and indirectness
    are provided as per-study or overall inputs. Outputs a pmatools object, a
    multi-outcome Summary of Findings table, and a full Appendix GRADE report
    in docx / html / pdf / md formats.
